headline: Lisa Vanderpump Throws an Epic Grand Opening Party For Pinky’s by Vanderpump at Flamingo Las Vegas
summary: LAS VEGAS, December 06, 2024--Guests were tickled pink at last night’s grand opening event for Lisa Vanderpump’s newest restaurant and cocktail bar, Pinky’s by Vanderpump, at Flamingo Las Vegas.
